name: Dinosaur Engineer
summary: Dive into 'Dinosaur Engineer', a VR adventure where futuristic metallic dinosaurs reign. Harness creativity in 'Dino Paint', guiding laser-toting dinos to craft canvas masterpieces. Engineer your beasts in 'DinoLab', customizing with an array of materials and defensive turrets. Test your skills in 'Battleground' with strategic ranged combat against armed dinosaur foes. Plus, get excited for the in-development 'Dino Boxing' – an exhilarating addition coming soon to our dino domain!"
